                     <join result="defendantPunishment" targOrder="Y" targets="t17830910-89-defend994 t17830910-89-punish490"></join>
               Imprisoned three months in Newgate
            </rs>.</p>
               <p>Tried by the London Jury before Mr. Justice ASHURST.</p>
